---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lang = 'zh';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<BaseLayout title="GAL Terre dell'Etna e dell'Alcantara | LQS Lab UniME" lang={lang}>
  <section class="relative py-20 lg:py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/cover-strategico-001.png`} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/10 via-transparent to-black/30"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="inline-block bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-white/10">
      <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">地方发展</span>
      <h1 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white mt-4 leading-tight">GAL Terre dell'Etna<br/>e dell'Alcantara</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mt-6 max-w-2xl">阅读过去，构建未来。26个合作市镇的地方发展计划。</p>
    </div></div>
  </section>
  <div class="gradient-line"></div>

  <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div><span class="text-xs font-mono text-dark-500 uppercase">类型</span><p class="text-dark-100 font-mono mt-1">GAL / LEADER</p></div>
          <div><span class="text-xs font-mono text-dark-500 uppercase">市镇</span><p class="text-dark-100 font-mono mt-1">26</p></div>
          <div><span class="text-xs font-mono text-dark-500 uppercase">人口</span><p class="text-dark-100 font-mono mt-1">175,278</p></div>
          <div><span class="text-xs font-mono text-dark-500 uppercase">面积</span><p class="text-dark-100 font-mono mt-1">965.52 km²</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="text-neon font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">项目</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">合作市镇发展计划</h2>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">GAL Terre dell'Etna e dell'Alcantara S.c.c.a.r.l. 是一个地方行动小组，在西西里PSP的LEADER干预框架内运作，促进一个非凡地区的综合地方发展：埃特纳火山东坡、阿尔坎塔拉河谷以及从贾尔迪尼纳克索斯到里波斯托的海岸线。</p>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">精益与质量解决方案实验室受委托编制<strong class="text-dark-100">地方发展计划（PSL）</strong>，该计划属于2023年12月30日第142号董事会决议批准的第1/2023号运营项目，题为<em>"埃特纳和阿尔坎塔拉之地的未来项目"</em>。</p>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">该项目产出了一项多层次科学地域研究，涉及合作伙伴关系中的全部26个市镇，对环境、社会经济、历史文化和基础设施背景进行了深入分析。</p>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed">该计划确立了中长期地域发展的全面、广泛和统一的愿景，在共享战略设计中定义统一的增长假设。确定干预路线、行动和项目，建立干预优先级。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 mb-16">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700">
          <img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/report-04.png`} alt="GAL 26个市镇地图" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="p-4 bg-dark-900"><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 italic">GAL Terre dell'Etna e dell'Alcantara的26个合作市镇，横跨卡塔尼亚省和墨西拿省。</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 mb-16">
        <span class="text-cyan font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">地域</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">火山与河流之间的独特遗产</h2>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">GAL地域面积965.52平方公里，位于西西里岛东部，地形以山地丘陵为主。包括阿尔坎塔拉河的整个水文盆地以及欧洲最高活火山埃特纳火山的北、东、南坡。</p>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">该地区拥有杰出的自然遗产：<strong class="text-dark-100">3个区域公园</strong>（埃特纳公园、内布罗迪山公园、阿尔坎塔拉河公园）、<strong class="text-dark-100">2个自然保护区</strong>和<strong class="text-dark-100">22个SCI和SPA保护区</strong>，保护面积46,460公顷，占总面积的48%。</p>
        <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-lg text-dark-100 mb-4">四大地域区</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-8">
          {[{img:'zona-costiera.png',name:'沿海区',desc:'从贾尔迪尼纳克索斯到里波斯托。旅游、港口基础设施、柑橘种植。'},{img:'zona-pedemontana.png',name:'山麓区',desc:'贾雷、马斯卡利、皮耶迪蒙特埃特内奥。葡萄种植、柑橘种植、城市中心。'},{img:'zona-valle.png',name:'阿尔坎塔拉河谷',desc:'弗兰卡维拉、卡斯蒂利奥内、兰达佐。河流公园、历史村庄、美食美酒。'},{img:'zona-montana.png',name:'山区',desc:'埃特纳和内布罗迪山坡。自然公园、徒步旅行、生物多样性。'}].map(z => (
            <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700">
              <img src={`/images/projects/gal-etna/${z.img}`} alt={z.name} class="w-full h-32 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="p-3 bg-dark-900"><p class="text-xs text-dark-100 font-bold">{z.name}</p><p class="text-[10px] text-dark-400 mt-1">{z.desc}</p></div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 text-sm">卡塔尼亚省（17个市镇）</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 mt-2">Calatabiano, Castiglione di Sicilia, Fiumefreddo di Sicilia, Giarre, Linguaglossa, Mascali, Milo, Nicolosi, Pedara, Piedimonte Etneo, Randazzo, Riposto, Sant'Alfio, Santa Venerina, Trecastagni, Viagrande, Zafferana Etnea</p></div>
          <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 text-sm">墨西拿省（9个市镇）</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 mt-2">Francavilla di Sicilia, Gaggi, Giardini-Naxos, Graniti, Malvagna, Moio Alcantara, Motta Camastra, Roccella Valdemone, Santa Domenica Vittoria</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mb-16">
        <span class="text-gold font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">方法论</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">多层次科学方法</h2>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">该研究采用严谨的地域分析方法，以四个互补维度构建，与国际可持续发展框架（2030议程、欧洲绿色协议、2023-2027共同农业政策）保持一致。</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          {[{icon:'01',title:'地域与环境',desc:'城市规划、交通基础设施、历史建筑、废弃村庄地图绘制、保护区普查、生物多样性评估。'},{icon:'02',title:'生产结构',desc:'按部门（农业、工业、服务业）全面企业普查，旅游深度分析：住宿容量和分类旅游服务。'},{icon:'03',title:'社会经济框架',desc:'通过劳动力市场和企业指标进行经济分析。通过人口和社会经济指数研究人口。按地方劳动系统划分地域。'},{icon:'04',title:'历史与传统',desc:'埃特纳和阿尔坎塔拉地区的历史经济和社会演变。关注古老手工艺和传统，分析地方认同。'}].map(item => (
            <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-neon/20 transition-colors">
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neon font-bold">{item.icon}</span>
              <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 mt-1">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400 mt-2">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mb-16">
        <span class="text-cyan font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">旅游</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">住宿基础设施</h2>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">旅游分析绘制了各市镇住宿设施的分布和容量地图。</p>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700">
          <img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/mappa-turismo.png`} alt="住宿设施地图" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="p-4 bg-dark-900"><p class="text-xs text-dark-400">各GAL市镇的床位容量和设施类型。</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mb-16">
        <span class="text-gold font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">卓越</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">卓越产业链和基础设施</h2>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">GAL地域拥有国际知名的农食产业链。埃特纳葡萄种植业拥有144家酒庄，分布在认证的Contrade上，代表了全球独一无二的火山土壤"英雄式"葡萄种植。</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700"><img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/mappa-etna-doc.jpg`} alt="Etna DOC葡萄酒地图" class="w-full h-72 object-cover" loading="lazy" /><div class="p-4 bg-dark-900"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 text-sm">Etna DOC葡萄酒</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 mt-1">认证的Contrade和附加地理单元。火山风土产出国际公认的独特葡萄酒。</p></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700"><img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/ferrovia-alcantara.jpg`} alt="阿尔坎塔拉-兰达佐铁路" class="w-full h-72 object-cover" loading="lazy" /><div class="p-4 bg-dark-900"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 text-sm">阿尔坎塔拉-兰达佐铁路</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 mt-1">历史铁路线（1959-1995，37公里），具有改建为自行车绿道的潜力。</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mb-16">
        <span class="text-neon font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">成果</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">研究产出</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700 bg-dark-900 flex flex-col"><div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden"><img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/cover-studio-page-001.png`} alt="研究报告封面" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100">科学地域研究</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 mt-1">地域系统现状报告。</p></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-dark-700 bg-dark-900 flex flex-col"><div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden"><img src={`${base}/images/projects/gal-etna/cover-strategico-001.png`} alt="战略计划封面" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100">战略计划</h3><p class="text-xs text-dark-400 mt-1">阅读过去，构建未来。</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          {[{num:'2',title:'交互式报告',desc:'可导航的网络仪表板，包含每个市镇的数据和指标。'},{num:'3a',title:'综合文件',desc:'面向决策者和利益相关者的研究发现运营摘要。'},{num:'3b',title:'立场文件',desc:'基于与相邻GAL比较分析的科学建议。'},{num:'4',title:'公开演示',desc:'向GAL合作伙伴展示成果（2025年5月15日）。'}].map(item => (
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-neon/20 transition-colors">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-dark-800 border border-neon/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-neon font-mono text-xs font-bold">{item.num}</span></div>
              <div><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100">{item.title}</h3><p class="text-sm text-dark-400 mt-1">{item.desc}</p></div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mb-16">
        <span class="text-cyan font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">战略</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-4">社区主导的地方发展战略</h2>
        <p class="text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">战略围绕三个基本轴心构建。</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-neon/20 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100">竞争力地域</h3><p class="text-sm text-dark-400 mt-2">地方产业链增值、中小企业创新、投资吸引、服务数字化。</p></div>
          <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-neon/20 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100">可持续地域</h3><p class="text-sm text-dark-400 mt-2">联合国教科文组织埃特纳遗产保护、生态转型、循环经济、可持续水资源管理。</p></div>
          <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-5 hover:border-neon/20 transition-colors"><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100">宜居地域</h3><p class="text-sm text-dark-400 mt-2">生活质量、对抗人口流失、废弃村庄再生、可持续交通。</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mb-16">
        <span class="text-neon font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">团队</span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-bold text-dark-100 mt-3 mb-6">工作组</h2>
        <div class="bg-dark-900 border border-dark-700 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 mb-3">科学协调</h3><ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-dark-400"><li><span class="text-neon font-mono text-xs">协调员</span> Giuseppe Ioppolo 教授</li><li>Michele Limosani 教授</li><li>Giuseppe Caristi 教授</li><li>Roberta Arbolino 教授</li><li>Katarzyna Szopik-Depczyńska 教授</li></ul></div>
            <div><h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] font-bold text-dark-100 mb-3">研究人员</h3><ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-dark-400"><li>Carlotta D'Alessandro 博士</li><li>Pietro Di Pietro 博士</li><li>Andrea Morana 博士</li></ul></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <a href="https://galetnaalcantara.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 border border-dark-600 hover:border-neon/50 text-dark-300 hover:text-neon font-medium rounded-lg transition-all hover:bg-neon/5 text-sm">GAL 网站 <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"></path></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
